directives.description:
The total weight of a query is the sum of the weights of all requested fields.  Requests exceeding the maximum
complexity will be rejected.

The weight of a submitted query and the maximum weight for a single request will be returned in the response in the
following format:

"extensions": {
  "weight": {
    "weight": 245,
    "maxWeight": 1000
  }
}

Fields with no weight directive have a default weight of 0
